    "title": "Daily Fresh Food Price Watch",
    "publishDate": "2026-05-02",
    "preheader": "Prices for staple fresh foods from chains that serve Beaufort County.",
    "intro": "This first pass compares like-for-like staples only. When a chain does not expose a stable public price for a matching item, it is left out rather than guessed. These links point to official store product pages, and some chain prices may still vary by store, pickup mode, or digital account context.",
    "methodology": [
      "Each section compares one normalized staple spec, not all versions of an item.",
      "Rankings use the cheapest exact public price we could verify on an official grocery site.",
      "Variable-weight meat listings can be tricky; if a chain exposes an average pack price more clearly than a stable local per-pound price, it is left out until we can normalize it confidently.",
      "Chains with Beaufort County stores but weak public item-level pricing are being tracked for future automation."
    ],
